continued the hungarians observed it and put the brakes on 
slowing the process 
gustavson said history may show the best solution to be 
czechoslovakias plan to distribute shares of stateowned property 
to its own citizens in the form of free or lowcost vouchers not 
transferable to foreigners until a later stage of reform 
