a federal judge struck down campaign 
contribution limits that california voters approved in 1988 a 
state election official warned against a fundraising frenzy 
before the nov 6 election 
a spokesman for the republican gubernatorial candidate us 
sen pete wilson challenged democratic candidate dianne feinstein 
the former san francisco mayor to join him in voluntarily adhering 
