cox predicted unhappily 
but ornstein said the ritualized lastminute hysteria messy as 
it may be generally produces compromises that have kept the 
deficit in check the solution may be to ignore the process he 
said because it stands up to close scrutiny about as well as 
sausagemaking 
the agreement we get is no less substantial he said but 
by the time it comes about were all nauseous 
