that much attention to arizona politics in new mexico 
udall said i ran in a very high profile hotly contested race 
in 1988 and we came within 5000 votes of taking an open 
congressional seat that race i think had an awful lot to do with 
my standing today i remember when i got in that primary in 1988 
my name identification and my standing in the polls was about 3 
percent 
there is no doubt that people know the udalls and know my 
fathers service to the country and they also ask about it many 
times on the campaign trail he said its usually out of 
admiration for what they have done 
