countries has restored about twothirds of the 48 million daily 
barrels of oil production removed from world markets by iraqs 
takeover of kuwait on aug 2 and the world embargo against 
iraqikuwaiti oil 
the united states uses more than 17 million barrels a day about 
half of it imported 
