while differing on some points and without seeking to change or 
convert one another benefits come in just getting to know and 
appreciate one another he said 
mormons hold some distinctive beliefs but like other 
christians they regard the bible as holy scripture honor christ 
as gods divine son uphold his teachings and believe in salvation 
through his atoning death and resurrection 
through candid dialogue participants learn from each other 
keller said out of the depth of spirituality i can learn so 
