the bus to a west hartford mall to shop at the sageallen there 
all the stores are going out there she said whos coming 
in here 
she shook her head as she reminisced about downtown when it 
bustled with department stores cafeterias and fiveanddimes 
it looks like its on the way out she said completely 
out 
