were being included in the discussions along with the gulf 
cooperation council of persian gulf countries 
the administration received assurances monday from 
policysetting panels of the imf and the world bank that both 
agencies stood ready to accelerate their lending activities in 
order to cushion the economic fallout from the doubling of world 
oil prices 
while the administration has focused its fundraising efforts 
primarily on egypt turkey and jordan officials of the imf and the 
